    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The Fuma may be known for their Shuriken but they are masters of all Ninja Tools. You may attach Paper Bombs to any weapon with the Thrown Keyword, not just Kunai. At 3rd Level, you may also attach Battle Wire to weapons with the Thrown property and give it the Returning Keyword and at 7th level, weapons you attach a Battle Wire to also gain the grapple property.</p>",
